{{le|1960年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1960 Formula One season|1960年}}，26歲的蘇爾特斯加入{{le|連花車隊 (1954年)|Team Lotus|連花車隊}}轉換跑道至四輪賽車賽事，在舉辦於[[銀石賽道|銀石賽道]]的1960年{{le|英國車手俱樂部國際盃|BRDC International Trophy}}初登場。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/obituary-john-surtees-1934-2017-881549/ |first=Adam |last=Cooper |title=Obituary: John Surtees, 1934-2017 |date=2017-03-10 |website=motorsport.com |accessdate=2017-03-12|language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312195940/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/obituary-john-surtees-1934-2017-881549/ |archivedate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.formula2.net/F160_6.htm |title=XII B.R.D.C. Daily Express International Trophy 1960 |website=formula2.net |accessdate=2017-03-12 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201956/http://www.formula2.net/F160_6.htm |archivedate=2016-03-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>很快地，在他的第二場一級方程式賽車賽事{{le|1960年英國大獎賽|1960 British Grand Prix}}便取得第二名的成績，接著又在第三場比賽{{le|1960年葡萄牙大獎賽|1960 Portuguese Grand Prix}}奪下[[桿位|桿位]]。<ref name="Formula 1 Hall of Fame"/>蘇爾特斯在{{le|1961年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1961 Formula One season|1961年}}加入由{{le|瑞吉·帕內爾|Reg Parnell}}掌管的{{le|約曼信用車隊|Yeoman Credit Racing}}並駕駛低底盤版庫珀T53，隨後，在{{le|1962年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1962 Formula One season|1962年}}改效力同樣由瑞吉·帕內爾掌管的{{le|約曼信用車隊|Yeoman Credit Racing|鮑梅克車隊}}，但這次則駕駛搭載V8引擎的羅拉Mk4。{{le|1963年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1963 Formula One season|1963年}}，蘇爾特斯轉隊至[[法拉利車隊|法拉利]]，接著在{{le|1964年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1964 Formula One season|1964年}}幫助該隊取得[[F1世界車手冠軍列表|車手世界冠軍]]及[[一級方程式世界車隊冠軍列表|車隊世界冠軍]]。<ref name="Formula 1 Hall of Fame"/><ref name="John Surtees Formula One statistics">{{cite web |url=http://www.4mula1.ro/history/driver/John_Surtees |title=John Surtees Formula One statistics |publisher=4mula1.ro |accessdate=2011-10-07 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927235959/http://www.4mula1.ro/history/driver/John_Surtees |archivedate=2011-09-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

1965年9月25日，蘇爾特斯在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略|安大略]]莫斯波特賽道（{{lang|en|Mosport Circuit}}）練習時，他駕駛的{{le|羅拉T70|Lola T70}}跑車前懸吊斷裂，導致撞車而遭遇一起嚴重事故。<ref name="Formula 1 Hall of Fame"/>作家A·J·貝姆（{{lang|en|A.J. Baime}}）便在他的著作《地獄駕駛》（''{{lang|en|Go Like Hell}}''）中提到，蘇爾特斯在兩側身體相差4英寸的情況下逃出事故現場。<ref name="Go Like Hell: Ford, Ferrari and their Battle for Speed and Glory at Le Mans">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4ddp0G3z-y0C |title=Go Like Hell: Ford, Ferrari and their Battle for Speed and Glory at Le Mans |last=Baime |first=A. J. |publisher=Random House |year=2011 |isbn=9781446497463 |page=262 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-14 |archive-date=2019-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831213849/https://books.google.com/books?id=4ddp0G3z-y0C |dead-url=no }}</ref>醫師針對大部分的骨折部位進行非手術治療，再加上少部分的物理伸展，直到左右兩側身體的差距少於1英寸。

{{le|1966年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1966 Formula One season|1966年賽季}}，一級方程式賽車將引擎最大排氣量限制提高至3公升。<ref name="Collection Editions: Ferrari In Formula One">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kW5eCAAAQBAJ&pg=PT143 |title=Collection Editions: Ferrari In Formula One |last=Buckland |first=Damien |publisher=Lulu Press, Inc |year=2015 |isbn=9781326174880 |page=143 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-14 |archive-date=2019-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831213847/https://books.google.com/books?id=kW5eCAAAQBAJ&pg=PT143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>蘇爾特斯在舉辦於銀石的1966年英國車手俱樂部國際盃駕駛法拉利的新車登場，最終，以落後[[傑克·布拉漢姆|傑克·布拉漢姆]]些微的差距取得第2名。<ref name="drivetribe">{{Cite web |url=https://drivetribe.com/p/LH6KT4zPQkWlMb-RghZ9aQ?iid=FN0CDG18S46vt88tmzXYng |title=Of His Own Construction - 1966 Repco Brabham BT19 |last=Masin |first=Michael  |website=drivetribe.com |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312055841/https://drivetribe.com/p/LH6KT4zPQkWlMb-RghZ9aQ?iid=FN0CDG18S46vt88tmzXYng |archivedate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>一週後的{{le|1966年摩納哥大獎賽|1966 Monaco Grand Prix|摩納哥大獎賽}}，蘇爾特斯在大直道上比駕駛2公升{{le|不列顛車隊|British Racing Motors|BRM}}的[[傑奇·史都華|傑奇·史都華]]具有絕對優勢，但是，隨後因為引擎故障而將領先地位拱手讓人。兩週後，{{le|1966年比利時大獎賽|1966 Belgian Grand Prix|比利時大獎賽}}的暴雨使得超過半數車手因事故退賽，桿位起跑的蘇爾特斯順利跑完比賽拿下分站冠軍。<ref name="Real Racers">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=cPAhDg87jz4C&pg=PA137 |title=Real Racers |last=Codling |first=Stuart |publisher=MBI Publishing Company |isbn=9781610597395 |page=137 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-14 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903032553/https://books.google.com/books?id=cPAhDg87jz4C&pg=PA137 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

由於義大利長期的罷工，法拉利在1966年[[利曼24小時耐力賽|利曼24小時耐力賽]]派出的車輛從原先的3輛減少為2輛（法拉利P3）。根據1966年利曼賽的規則，每輛車僅允許由2位車手輪流駕駛，<ref name="John Surtees: Former F1 world champion was a towering figure"/>法拉力派出的第一隊由[[麥克·帕克斯|麥克·帕克斯]]及[[盧多維科·斯卡爾菲奧蒂|盧多維科·斯卡爾菲奧蒂]]駕駛，第二隊則為{{le|尚·紀謝|Jean Guichet}}及{{le|洛倫佐·班蒂尼|Lorenzo Bandini}}，蘇爾特斯則被從參賽陣容中剔除。<ref name="John Surtees: Former F1 world champion was a towering figure"/>當蘇爾特斯詢問身為車隊經理兼領隊的{{link-de|歐金尼奧·德拉戈尼|Eugenio Dragoni}}自己無法出賽的原因時，德拉戈尼表示他認為蘇爾特斯在1965年末的傷勢還未痊癒，不足以應付一場長達24小時的耐力賽。<ref name="John Surtees: Former F1 world champion was a towering figure"/>蘇爾特斯對此原因深感不滿，不久後便選擇離隊。<ref name="John Surtees: Former F1 world champion was a towering figure">{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35126201 |title=John Surtees: Former F1 world champion was a 'towering figure' |last=Benson |first=Andrew |access-date= 2017-03-11 |work=BBC |date= 2017-03-10|language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312175631/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35126201 |archivedate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>他在剩餘的賽季為[[庫珀汽車公司|庫珀]]-[[瑪莎拉蒂|瑪莎拉蒂]]出賽，拿下賽季收官站的分站冠軍，並在年度車手積分榜上名列第2，將車手冠軍拱手讓給傑克·布拉漢姆。<ref name="Complete Encyclopedia of Formula One">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mXRZ9OvEsWgC&pg=PA35 |title=Complete Encyclopedia of Formula One: Presenting the Drivers, Cars, Circuits and Every |publisher=Parragon Pubishing India |isbn=9781445405353 |page=35 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2019-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831140013/https://books.google.com/books?id=mXRZ9OvEsWgC&pg=PA35 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的這項決定也讓法拉利喪失爭奪1966年世界冠軍的機會。賽季結束後，法拉利屈居亞軍並將車隊冠軍讓給了[[布拉漢姆|布拉漢姆]]-{{le|雷普科|Repco}}。<ref name="Formula 1 Hall of Fame"/><ref>{{Cite book |title=Go Like Hell: Ford, Ferrari, and Their Battle for Speed and Glory at Le Mans|url=https://archive.org/details/golikehellfordfe0000baim_z5z9|first=A.J. |last=Baime |publisher=Houghton Mifflin Harcourt |year=2009 |isbn=978-0-618-82219-5}}</ref>

1966年，蘇爾特斯參加首屆{{le|加拿大－美國挑戰盃|Can-Am}}，<ref name="Aston Martin: Power, Beauty and Soul">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UnNUiPWfnvQC&pg=PT21 |title=Aston Martin: Power, Beauty and Soul |last=Dowsey |first=David |publisher=Images Publishing |year=2010 |isbn=9781864704242 |edition=illustrated |page=21 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2019-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824165518/https://books.google.com/books?id=UnNUiPWfnvQC&pg=PT21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="The encyclopaedia of motor racing">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Zp3ZAAAAMAAJ |title=The encyclopaedia of motor racing |last=Davey |first=Keith |publisher=D. McKay Co. |year=1969 |page=182 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829133753/https://books.google.com/books?id=Zp3ZAAAAMAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在6場分站中取得3場勝利，<ref name="George Eaton">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lifwAAAAMAAJ |title=George Eaton: Five Minutes to Green: The Anatomy of a Young Canadian Auto Racer's First Season as a Professional Driver in Competitive Cars |last=Orr |first=Frank |publisher=Longman Canada |year=1970 |pages=21 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903083255/https://books.google.com/books?id=lifwAAAAMAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>積分超越另外三位分站冠軍[[丹·葛尼|丹·葛尼]]（羅拉）、{{le|馬克·多洛修|Mark Donohue}}（羅拉）及[[菲爾·希爾|菲爾·希爾]]（{{le|查普拉汽車|Chaparral Cars|查普拉}}），以及麥拉倫的[[布魯斯·麥克拉倫|布魯斯·麥克拉倫]]與[[克里斯·阿蒙|克里斯·阿蒙]]，最終，蘇爾特斯贏得總冠軍。<ref name="Lola T70: The Racing History and Individual Chassis Record">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dJjsAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA46 |title=Lola T70: The Racing History and Individual Chassis Record |last=Starkey |first=John |publisher=Veloce Publishing Ltd |year=2002 |isbn=9781903706138 |edition=illustrated |page=46 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2019-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831120444/https://books.google.com/books?id=dJjsAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA46 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1966年12月，蘇爾特斯與[[本田車隊|本田]]簽約。<ref>{{cite journal |date= 1966-12-01 |title=Surtees settles for Honda |journal=Auto News |publisher=Motor Cycle News Ltd |location=Peterborough |issue=31 |language=en }}</ref>在效力該隊的首場比賽{{le|1967年南非大獎賽|1967 South African Grand Prix}}取得第3名後，他所駕駛的{{le|本田RA273|Honda RA273}}遭遇一系列的機械故障問題。蘇爾特斯在{{le|1967年義大利大獎賽|1967 Italian Grand Prix|義大利大獎賽}}駕駛全新坐駕{{le|本田RA300|Honda RA300}}，以相距傑克·布拉漢姆0.2秒之差奪下本田的第2座一級方程式賽車分站冠軍。最終，蘇爾特斯在1967年車手積分榜上名列第4。<ref name="John Surtees Formula One statistics"/>

同年，蘇爾特斯在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]附近的{{le|河濱國際賽道|Riverside International Raceway|河濱}}參加{{le|美國汽車俱樂部|United States Auto Club}}舉辦的季末公路賽—雷克斯·梅斯300印第賽（{{lang|en|Rex Mays 300}}）。這場賽事的參賽者通常是在橢圓型賽道具有一定經驗的頂尖美國車手，像是同為一級方程式賽車車手的[[吉姆·克拉克|吉姆·克拉克]]與丹·葛尼。<ref name="Auto Driver">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=Klc7AAAAMAAJ |title=Auto Driver |publisher=Counterpoint |year=1967 |volume=67 |page=123 |language=en |access-date=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903083256/https://books.google.co.in/books?id=Klc7AAAAMAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

{{le|1970年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1970 Formula One season|1970年}}，蘇爾特斯自己成立了一支車隊{{le|蘇爾特斯車隊|Surtees}}，作為製造商參賽{{le|方程式5000|Formula 5000}}、[[二級方程式|二級方程式]]及一級方程式賽車，共9個賽季。<ref name="Formula 1 Hall of Fame"/>他在{{le|1972年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1972 Formula One season|1972年}}退役，他的車隊也在該年靠著{{le|麥克·海伍德|Mike Hailwood}}贏得歐洲二級方程式錦標賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.formula2.net/F272_Tables.htm |title=1972 Formula Two results |publisher=formula2.net |accessdate=2011-10-07 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202054842/http://formula2.net/F272_Tables.htm |archivedate=2017-02-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>此後，蘇爾特斯車隊在{{le|1978年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1978 Formula One season|1978年}}宣告解散。<ref name="independent">{{Cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/motor-racing/john-surtees-dead-f1-world-champion-motorbike-aged-83-a7623281.html |title=John Surtees dead: Former F1 and motorbike world champion dies, aged 83 |access-date=2017-03-10 |first=Jack |last=de Menezes |work=The Independent |date= 2017-03-10 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312072553/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/motor-racing/john-surtees-dead-f1-world-champion-motorbike-aged-83-a7623281.html |archivedate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

=== 一級方程式賽車退役後生涯 ===
[[File:John_Surtees_at_Goodwood_Revival_2011_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]
1970年代，蘇爾特斯曾在倫敦南部的{{le|西威克姆|West Wickham}}經營一家摩托車店，也曾在[[肯特郡|肯特郡]][[埃登布里奇|埃登布里奇]]做本田汽車的經銷商。<ref name="surreymirror">{{Cite news |url=http://www.surreymirror.co.uk/8203-surrey-born-f1-and-world-motorcycle-champion-john-surtees-has-died/story-30195218-detail/story.html |title=Surrey racing legend John Surtees who won F1 and world motorcycle championships has died |first=Luke |last=Jarmyn |work=Surrey Mirror |date=2017-03-10 |access-date=2017-03-10 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316132155/http://www.surreymirror.co.uk/8203-surrey-born-f1-and-world-motorcycle-champion-john-surtees-has-died/story-30195218-detail/story.html |archivedate=2017-03-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>他仍舊持續駕駛著他的古董車，參加各類摩托車賽事。此外，他亦未完全脫離單人座賽車界，在2005至2007年間，擔任[[A1GP汽車大獎賽|A1GP汽車大獎賽]]{{le|A1大獎賽英國隊|A1 Team Great Britain|英國隊}}的主席。<ref name="bbc"/>他的兒子{{le|亨利·蘇爾特斯|Henry Surtees}}繼承父親的衣缽，參加了{{le|國際汽聯二級方程式錦標賽 (2009年建立)|FIA Formula Two Championship (established in 2009)|國際汽聯二級方程式錦標賽}}、{{le|英國雷諾方程式錦標賽|British Formula Renault Championship}}及[[寶馬方程式|英國寶馬方程式]]錦標賽等賽事，<ref>{{cite web |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/6946783.stm |title= How to become F1 champion |accessdate= 2007-08-22 |date= 2007-08-22 |first = Sarah |last=Holt |publisher = bbc.co.uk |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071021030230/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/6946783.stm |archivedate=2007-10-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>但是，卻在2009年7月19日於布蘭茲·哈奇出賽二級方程式錦標賽時意外逝世。<ref>{{cite news |title=John Surtees' son Henry killed in Formula Two accident |first=Tom |last=Cary |work=The Telegraph |date=2009-07-19 |accessdate=2011-10-07 |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/5866783/John-Surtees-son-Henry-killed-in-Formula-Two-accident.html |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629110115/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/5866783/John-Surtees-son-Henry-killed-in-Formula-Two-accident.html |archivedate=2016-06-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

1996年，蘇爾特斯入選[[國際賽車名人堂|國際賽車名人堂]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://motorsportshalloffame.com/main/03_halloffame.htm |title=John Surtees at the International Motorsports Hall of Fame |publisher=motorsportshalloffame.com |accessdate=2011-10-07 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228013758/http://motorsportshalloffame.com/main/03_halloffame.htm |archivedate=2013-12-28 |deadurl= }}</ref>國際摩托車賽車協會在2003年授予他大獎賽「傳奇車手」的榮耀。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.motogp.com/en/MotoGP+Legends |title=MotoGP Legends |publisher=motogp.com |accessdate=2011-10-07 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119183854/http://www.motogp.com/en/MotoGP%2BLegends |archivedate=2017-01-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>原先持有[[員佐勳章|員佐勳章]]（MBE）的他又在{{le|2008年壽辰授勳|Birthday Honours}}獲頒[[官佐勳章|官佐勳章]]（OBE），<ref>{{London Gazette |issue=58729 |date=2008-06-14 |startpage=13 |supp=yes}}</ref>接著在{{le|2016年新年授勳|2016 New Year Honours}}受封[[司令勳章|司令勳章]]（CBE），以表彰在賽車領域的貢獻。<ref name="theguardian"/><ref>{{LondonGazette|issue=61450|supp=yes|startpage=N10|endpage=|date=2015-12-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/489049/NY2016HonoursFullList.pdf |title = New Year's Honours 2016 |work= GOV.UK |publisher= Her Majesty's Stationery Office |date= 2015-12-30 |accessdate= 2015-12-30|language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170114132859/https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/489049/NY2016HonoursFullList.pdf |archivedate=2017-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

蘇爾特斯在2013年獲頒{{le|西格雷夫獎|Segrave Trophy}}，以表揚他贏得多座世界冠軍，且是目前歷史上唯一在兩輪及四輪賽事皆獲得世界冠軍的車手。<ref name="incheshiremagazine">{{Cite news |url=http://incheshiremagazine.co.uk/segrave-trophy-awarded-to-john-surtees-obe/ |title=Segrave Trophy awarded to John Surtees OBE |access-date=2017-03-10 |work=INCheshire Magazine |date=2017-03-08|language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312051433/http://incheshiremagazine.co.uk/segrave-trophy-awarded-to-john-surtees-obe/ |archivedate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

2015年，[[牛津布魯克斯大學|牛津布魯克斯大學]]頒授蘇爾特斯[[工程學博士|工程學博士]][[名譽學位|名譽學位]]。<ref name="johnsurtees">{{Cite web |url=http://www.johnsurtees.com/?p=364 |title=John Surtees Receives Honorary Degree by Oxford Brookes |website=johnsurtees.com |date=2015-06-23 |access-date=2017-03-10 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312063500/http://www.johnsurtees.com/?p=364 |archivedate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="brookes">{{Cite web |url=https://www.brookes.ac.uk/about-brookes/honorary-graduates/list-by-year/ |title=Honorary Graduates |website=Oxford Brookes University |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316133338/https://www.brookes.ac.uk/about-brookes/honorary-graduates/list-by-year/ |archivedate=2017-03-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

=== 個人生活 ===
蘇爾特斯有過兩段婚姻：他在1962年與派翠西亞·柏克（{{lang|en|Patricia Burke}}）結婚，兩人於1979年離婚；他在住院期間認識了病房護理長珍·斯帕羅（{{lang|en|Jane Sparrow}}），兩人於1987年結婚並育有兩女一子：莉奧諾拉（{{lang|en|Leonora}}）、艾德文娜（{{lang|en|Edwina}}）及亨利（{{lang|en|Henry}}）。<ref name="John Surtees obituary">{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/mar/10/john-surtees-obituary |title=John Surtees obituary |first=Alan |last=Henry |access-date=2017-03-10 |work=The Guardian |date=2017-03-10|language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315144414/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/mar/10/john-surtees-obituary |archivedate=2017-03-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

=== 逝世 ===
2017年3月10日，蘇爾特斯因呼吸衰竭病逝於[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[聖喬治醫院|聖喬治醫院]]，享壽83歲。<ref name="bbc">{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39235608 |title=John Surtees: Former F1 world champion dies at 83 |access-date=2017-03-10 |work=BBC |date=2017-03-10|language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312133210/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39235608 |archivedate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="theguardian">{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/mar/10/john-surtees-formula-one-dies |title=John Surtees, former F1 and motorcycle world champion, dies aged 83  |first=Giles |last=Richards |access-date=2017-03-10 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2017-03-10|language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314224220/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/mar/10/john-surtees-formula-one-dies |archivedate=2017-03-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

